headline: Live Nation downgraded at Rothschild on margin slowdown, DOJ lawsuit overhang
summary: Investing.com -- Rothschild downgraded Live Nation to Neutral from Buy, saying the concert promoter’s margin expansion is set to slow after 2025, limiting room for further earnings upgrades at a time when the stock is trading at record highs.
